==English==
===Etymology===
{{confix|en|xero|phyte|t1=dry|t2=plant}}
===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|en|/ˈzɪəɹəʊfaɪt/}}
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{lb|en|botany}} Any [[plant]] suited for life in a [[habitat]] where [[water]] is [[scarce]], such as in a [[desert]] or [[chaparral]]. Such plants may be [[succulent]], have small or [[reduce]]d [[leaves]], or [[spine]]s.
# A [[desert]] [[plant]]
